Rishikesh → Kedarnath → Chopta → Auli → Badrinath → return via main highway
Why this order works best:

Kedarnath lies east of the Alaknanda, Chopta is directly on the natural connecting route.
Auli & Badrinath are both accessed through Joshimath, avoiding repeated climbs.
Uses NH‑7 / Char Dham highway, minimizing fuel & time loss.
Avoids zigzagging between Mandakini and Alaknanda valleys.


📍 Day‑wise Efficient Route Plan
Day 1: Rishikesh → Guptkashi

Distance: ~180 km
Time: 7–8 hrs
Route:
Rishikesh → Devprayag → Srinagar → Rudraprayag → Guptkashi
Overnight: Guptkashi / Sitapur
Smooth highway drive along Alaknanda & Mandakini rivers
 [uttarakhandtrips.com], [travelvaidya.com]


Day 2: Guptkashi → Gaurikund → Kedarnath

Road: Guptkashi → Sonprayag → Gaurikund (30 km)
Trek: 16 km (or helicopter optional)
Overnight: Kedarnath

This is the only access route to Kedarnath temple [chardhamyatra.org], [blog.yatradham.org]

Day 3: Kedarnath → Guptkashi

Trek: 16 km down
Drive: Back to Guptkashi
Recovery night (important for altitude management)


Day 4: Guptkashi → Chopta

Distance: ~45 km
Time: 2–3 hrs
Route:
Guptkashi → Ukhimath → Chopta
Overnight: Chopta

This is the shortest and most scenic connector between Kedarnath valley and upper Garhwal [blog.yatradham.org]

Day 5: Chopta → Joshimath (Auli base)

Early morning: Tungnath / Chandrashila trek (optional)
Distance: ~75 km
Time: 3.5–4 hrs
Route:
Chopta → Mandal → Gopeshwar → Chamoli → Joshimath
Overnight: Joshimath / Auli

This mountain shortcut reduces ~35 km compared to Rudraprayag route [travelvaidya.com]

Day 6: Auli (Local Sightseeing)

Ropeway, ski slopes, viewpoints
No major driving (fuel & fatigue saver)


Day 7: Joshimath → Badrinath → Joshimath

Distance: ~45 km one way
Time: 2 hrs each way
Route:
Joshimath → Vishnuprayag → Govindghat → Badrinath
Visit Mana Village
Return to Joshimath

Best road quality in the region due to Char Dham upgrades [travelvaidya.com], [vaayuaviation.com]

Day 8: Joshimath → Rishikesh (Return)

Distance: ~255 km
Time: 9–10 hrs
Route:
Joshimath → Karnaprayag → Rudraprayag → Srinagar → Rishikesh


