💡 Cost‑Saving Tips

Use shared taxis Guptkashi ↔ Gaurikund.
Stay in Joshimath instead of Auli (hotels cheaper).
Avoid Chopta detours after Joshimath (adds ~120 km extra).
Early starts reduce traffic delays on Char Dham route.

